{"tid":1923281,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)Ultraman Orb","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T04:37:17.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96c49abc3b36eb20399f49aa1c65a68d63984bb6","tid":1923281,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=0c7059db\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=9a4f1442\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f7740fdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/ce/Ultraman_Orb_Poster_resized.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fce%2FUltraman_Orb_Poster_resized.jpg&h=e08c1f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在遙遠的過去，出現了能夠毀滅世界的恐怖存在&mdash;&mdash;魔王獸，打算將一切破壞殆盡。但是，光之戰士超人力霸王們，封印了魔王獸，取回了宇宙的和平。<br />\n<br />\n時光流逝，環遊世界的流浪青年&mdash;&mdash;紅凱，使用名為Orb圓環的道具，借用傳說中的超人力霸王的力量，變身成為超人力霸王Orb，向復活的魔王獸發起了挑戰！ <br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=e9a114d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=5f986e6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1d4f610cb2856ebc5b1c7acce3916826a0f6ba","tid":1923281,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dd07b78765053c1887a8f679b25daa834d320d","tid":1923281,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616a39329b53fda8fd41a56327709e5c380fef44","tid":1923281,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" cla